title: (Mon Early Bird) The Hip Hop Cowboy Ryan Charles Shuts Brings Down the House + Morgan Reviews ‘Saved by the Bell’ + Is Lunchbox Wife Upset He Forgot Their Anniversary?
itunes:title: (Mon Early Bird) The Hip Hop Cowboy Ryan Charles Shuts Brings Down the House + Morgan Reviews ‘Saved by the Bell’ + Is Lunchbox Wife Upset He Forgot Their Anniversary?
description:
Fresh off of American Song Contest, Ryan Charles stops by the studio to talk about “New Boot Goofin”, life in Buffalo, Wyoming and how a DM led him to being on TV.  Morgan gives her “Millennial Review” after watching the first 8 episodes of Saved by the Bell because she’s never seen it. Does the show hold up? Lunchbox brings in audio of his wife’s reaction to him forgetting their anniversary but there’s a twist! Lunchbox left the room while she recorded the audio…so he hears it for the first time on the air with us. Was she actually upset??

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
